ess enables us to not only identify unique growth opportunities but also maintain our intimate knowledge of the companys financial and competitive position focus growth performance disclosure focus growth gips disclosure polen capital gips letter polen focus growth polen focus growth sma polen growth fund us mutual fund polen capital focus us growth fund ucits meet our teams we believe that we have a sustainable competitive advantage in our investment approach driven by our concentration longterm orientation and discipline dan davidowitz nbsp  nbsp cio  portfolio manager recent content      see the polen difference  portfolios project polen capital research download pdf allergan case study polen capital research download pdf st quarter  focus growth commentary download pdf recent media      view the polen difference how polen growth fund consistently beats the market view more polen capital launches international growth strategy download pdf polen capital featured as a best place to work view more phone          follow us mission about us advisory committee polen difference history best places to work citizenship careers philosophy investment philosophy focus growth global growth international growth us small company growth strategies focus growth global growth international growth us small company growth people insights media  nw corporate blvd suite  boca raton fl  fax        email infopolencapitalcom  copyright  polen capital all rights reserved  privacy  disclosures  sitemap polen capital focus global growth fund ucits  polen capital contact us mission about us about us advisory committee polen difference history best places to work citizenship careers philosophy investment philosophy focus growth global growth international growth us small company growth strategies focus growth global growth international growth us small company growth people insights media contact us investing in great global businessesfor the longterm polen capital focus global growth fund uc