quity portfolios the firm also manages limited partnerships and offshore funds for its clients it also launches and manages equity mutual funds for its clients the firm invests in the public equity markets of the united states it invests in growth stocks of largecap companies to create its portfolios the firm benchmarks the performance of its portfolios against the sp  index and russell  it employs a fundamental analysis combined with bottom up stock picking approach to make its investments polen capital management llc was founded in  and is based in boca raton florida detailed description  north military trailsuite boca raton fl united statesfounded in  phone  fax  wwwpolencapitalcom key executives for polen capital management llc mr stanley charles moss cpa cfa ceo  chief risk officer mr brian yacko manager of operations and trading mr daniel adam davidowitz cfa head of the large company growth team  focus growth portfolio manager mr andrew powers msmba director of information technology mr jim haymes cfa director of institutional relations compensation as of fiscal year  polen capital management llc key developments polen capital appoints jeff mueller as coportfolio manager on global growth strategy jul   polen capital announced that jeff mueller has been named coportfolio manager of the firms global growth strategy mueller joined the companys growth team in  as a research associate and was promoted to research analyst shortly after his hiring he will manage the portfolio collaboratively with lead portfolio manager julian pick who launched the global growth strategy in  prior to joining the company mr mueller spent  years in the us marine corps during which he logged over  hours flying combat missions in fas polen capital plans opening of boston office appoints tucker walsh as head of small company growth team jun   polen capital announced that it has launched a us small company growth strategy and that tucker walsh will join the firm to lead a small company team