ministrator at polen capital management llc overview relationships paths career history denise avila office administrator at polen capital management llc overview number of relationships this person is connected to  people relationships see details stan c moss chief executive officer at polen capital management llc dan davidowitz head of the large company growth team  focus growth portfolio manager at polen capital management llc todd morris international growth portfolio manager  analyst at polen capital management llc jim haymes director of institutional relations at polen capital management llc nickolas mark director of finance at polen capital management llc andrew powers director of information technology at polen capital management llc brandon p ladoff director of research  analystlarge company growth team at polen capital management llc damon anson ficklin focus growth portfolio manager  analyst at polen capital management llc jeff mueller coportfolio manager global growth strategy at polen capital management llc kevin c schneider director of operations at polen capital management llc see  more listings with relsci professional start my free trial ➤ see  more paths to denise avila denise avila you connections via relationship science denise avila sync your contacts to see how you can connect with denise avila start my free trial ➤ see more career history office administrator current polen capital management llc polen capital management pcm employs disciplined bottomup concentrated us global and international equity investment strategies that focus on highquality largecap growth investments the polen focus growth strategy invests in a portfolio of companies pcm believes can deliver midteens earnings per share growth over the next  years while incurring only moderate risk the strategy invests in a concentrated portfolio of primarily largecap us common stocks with sustainable competitive advantages the polen growth fund is a us largecap us growth fund that emphasizes sustainable earnings growth and focuses on companies with high returns on capital and double digit earnings growth it is a concentrated portfolio of approximately  highquality growth companies with low portfolio turnover and longterm holding periodspcms global growth strategy is similar to their focus growth strategy but with adjustments to compensate for fundamental and macroeconomic influences that may have a greater effect on the relative performance of foreign stocks than domestic issues it invests in a concentrated portfolio of outstanding us and international businesses with competitive advantages and the potential for sustained superior growth the polen global growth fund emphasizes sustainable earnings growth and focuses on companies with high returns on capital and double digit earnings growth it is a concentrated portfolio of approximately  highquality growth companies with low portfolio turnover and longterm holding periodsthe polen international growth strategy applies the same philosophy as the focus growth and global growth portfolios but invests exclusively in businesses domiciled outside of the us adjustments are made to compensate for macroeconomic and countryspecific influences that can impact the relative performance of foreign stocks the strategy invests in a concentrated portfolio of primarily largecap nonus businesses with competitive advantages and the potential for sustained superior growth the polen capital international growth fund seeks to achieve longterm growth of capital with with pcms active share investment process that relies on indepth research to uncover competitivelyadvantaged companies that meet their disciplined investment criteria other affiliations denise avila is affiliated with polen capital management llc youve reached your  free profiles limit this month upgrade to relsci pro today to enjoy unlimited article views and much more start my free trial ➤ still not convinced check out our full listing of features here are 